>> time required: 4 hours
>> course: side
>> serves: 8

Soak @dried pinto beans{450%g} in water overnight
Add beans quartered @onion{1} and smashed @garlic cloves{3} to a pan
Cover with water and season with salt
Simmer covered for ~{30%minutes}
Uncover and continue cooking ~{90%minutes} or until soft
Heat @lard{1/4%cup} and add beans and broth, smash until creamy
